His 32-year-old wife Shamina Yousuf, a secretary from Edgware, also in north west London, is charged with trafficking into the country and ABH.

Ghanian national Shashi Kala Obhrai, 53, an optician, of Northwood, Middlesex, is charged with trafficking within the UK, ABH and making threats to kill.

Her husband Balram Kumar Obhrai, 58, a computer entrepreneur, of Northwood, Middlesex, is accused of trafficking into the UK and making threats to kill.

